"1734c30a6a22f8eeb53abd2eae44d9efd9914fed","tid":1632494,"uid":284304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:29:17.000Z","msg":"我地唔會割席 但現實文宣做到既野好有限<br />\n前線參考下要點做吧<br />\n1.美國左膠大愛支援路線<br />\n2.香港經濟攬炒路線"},{"pid":"a2267c5dce986ae7b8206ce1d4f1580bbbcf81a0","tid":1632494,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744830680bd5724e9b24081c8402d5ff91a177cb","tid":1632494,"uid":65089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:30:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"39727b49a5b8f1222cd595b3f9e4ae2cf06879f1","tid":1632494,"uid":284304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:30:48.000Z","msg":"我必須嚴肅咁講<br />\n不經思考既道歉係同割席冇分別<br />\n你亂咁道歉姐係代表你既行動係冇思考過 <br />\n政治層面上反效果更大<br />\n(你想像下點解黑警到今日一次道歉都冇就知)"},{"pid":"6d4afa2b5050d443060be66621f5a9ccfc0d3b80","tid":1632494,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b3efbe54fb672d9650bff1156a77fa823cb603","tid":1632494,"uid":89974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:31:22.000Z","msg":"裝修係用黎令商家向政府施壓，<br />\n政府被施壓一係就跪一係就加辣<br />\n一加辣人權法就更易過<br />\n<br />\n我理解唔到合理裝修明明成效咁大但係大家為咗明明可以用文宣補救8成既所謂國際民意(仲要未FC)而叫前線收手，仲未計你係連登根本叫唔到前線收手<br />\n<br />\n如果要苦行僧賣慘，咁多條浮屍碎屍骨折仲唔夠慘？"},{"pid":"27ee783b8760133b341d149c3b0efb964b061b09","tid":1632494,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c292d171d4ec226994c1dc55460e7d8356eb751","tid":1632494,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7a7951da80b62a156880daca09514b2d