,"uid":159417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"62b9a00c3b4ba020b3d3791a3118732e7f76b05e","tid":1632494,"uid":136038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:49:23.000Z","msg":"唔好再拆野裝修得唔得<br />\n好難同人兜㗎<br />\n你自己圍內就好撚爽<br />\n人地點睇？<br />\n香港人就話知咩事可以當睇唔到冷處理<br />\n國際戰線唯有洗多啲警暴片<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即係用人血嚟洗你做嘅野！</span><br />\n你打爛野咪打囉<br />\n你打人咪打囉<br />\n做乜春擺上檯面俾人睇？<br />\n十鳩幾個記者影撚住重拆重打<br />\n車人嗰啲打完全冇問題<br />\n俾人影到博出鏡英雄主義？<br />\n有啲野係要美化㗎<br />\n唔係話要做左膠散播失敗主義<br />\n係一定有臥底煽動，但係都有自己友囉<br />\n唔識檢討鬧我五毛分化割蓆都要講"},{"pid":"b428bb251ba91805be29c7be41ad9546c78be4d7","tid":1632494,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"前線有狗扮人，連登都好多五毛搵冥通<br />\n另外都有mon po狗，係吖，講緊你隻死肥閪mon po狗<br />\n<br />\n乳旗同五毛玩，不過去接任務<br />\n勇武手足都唔好理咁多好明顯嘅分化po, 笑下算<br />\n好明顯有鬼想攪到雨傘咁分化，一直係共狗手段之一<br />\n<br />\n個個人都知不割𥱊，不篤灰，不指責<br />\n係狗先唔識字唔理解<br />\n<br />\n短期係要諗計幫：<br />\n1蒙面法司法覆核<br />\n2人權法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma